data.title: Mrs. Leslie Anderson
data.text:
I am originally from Guatemala but Tallahassee is my home now. I went to FSU where I met my husband. We have two wonderful kids, Bianca and RG who are the love of my life.

At home, I like to read, garden and do "DIY" projects for my house. When I am not playing "Bob the builder", I spend most of my time in my new art studio. I finally have a place where I can feel creative and work on my own work!!!!!!.

I like to travel and learn about people's cultures and traditions.
